---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const daysTo = Math.ceil((new Date('2026-07-31').getTime() - Date.now()) / 86400000);
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			
			<h1>Hello, Fella!</h1>
			<p>
				This is my own personal Page I'll be using for different things such as posting some Blogs, tracking my own progress, posting some useful resources for myself and others, and a lot of other stuff. If you've found this in the bio of my discord, through Star Logistics, Project SP itself or through any other means, feel free to take a look if you care, though most of the stuff that will be posted here won't be useful nor interesting to you.
			</p>
			<b> {daysTo} </b> days left of Project Star's clock, Cycle One.

			<br> 

			<br> <i> If you're interested about collaborating on any creative, self-improvement, or otherwise projects of mine or your own contact me. I'm willing to hear you out on both joining me, or vice-versa. </b>

		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
